    "The detailed development of this database has been described elsewhere 28 and the code base to reproduce the database is given in the corresponding Github repository 29.",
    "The Elsevier API was used to extract around 20 million image captions from Elsevier publications.",
    "The data extraction task was focused solely on the abstracts and figure captions within the corpus.",
    "Due to the nature of the role that they serve within the paper, these sections tend to be highly focused and contain very little information peripheral to the main hypothesis of the study 2, 3.",
    "This is relevant for the subsequent relation determination task which relies on a statistical count of triples and hence can be easily biased by noise from other sections."
